      "scene_id": "scene_001",
      "scene_number": 1,
      "text": "EXT. ANCIENT SKYBRIDGE \u2013 ABOVE THE CLOUDS \u2013 DAWN\n\n[Approx. Timestamp: 00:00:00]\n\nA colossal STONE BRIDGE stretches between two floating mountain ranges, suspended miles above rolling clouds. Wind HOWLS. Sunlight breaks through mist, painting the bridge in gold.\n\nA weathered expedition airship hovers nearby.",
