    {
      "scene_id": "scene_002",
      "scene_number": 2,
      "text": "INT. AIRSHIP \u2013 CONTINUOUS\n\n[00:01:30]\n\nMeet the team:\n\nARJUN (32) \u2013 Calm, sharp, seasoned explorer\n\nMIRA (29) \u2013 Historian, emotionally driven\n\nROOK (35) \u2013 Muscular climber, dry humor\n\nTAVI (19) \u2013 Young drone pilot, curious and reckless\n\nThey gear up.\n\nMIRA\n(awed)\nThe Skybridge of Aeralis\u2026 People thought it was a myth.\n\nARJUN\nEvery myth starts as a warning.",
      "start": 90.0,
      "end": 113.6,
      "duration": 23.6,
