    {
      "scene_id": "scene_003",
      "scene_number": 3,
      "text": "EXT. SKYBRIDGE ENTRANCE \u2013 MOMENTS LATER\n\n[00:03:00]\n\nAncient runes glow faintly beneath their boots as they step onto the bridge.\n\nThe bridge CREAKS \u2014 not weak, but alive.\n\nTAVI\nTell me it\u2019s not going to collapse.\n\nROOK\nIf it does, you won\u2019t hear me scream. Wind\u2019ll steal it first.\n\nThey move forward.",
      "start": 180.0,
      "end": 200.8,
      "duration": 20.8,
