    {
      "scene_id": "scene_004",
      "scene_number": 4,
      "text": "EXT. SKYBRIDGE \u2013 MIDSPAN\n\n[00:06:00]\n\nThe bridge widens into a platform. Massive stone statues of forgotten guardians line the sides.\n\nSuddenly\u2014\nA LOW RUMBLE.\n\nThe statues\u2019 eyes glow.\n\nMIRA\n(reading runes)\n\u201cIt judges those who cross.\u201d\n\nStone arms SHIFT slightly.\n\nARJUN\nThen walk with purpose.",
      "start": 360.0,
      "end": 378.0,
