      "scene_id": "scene_006",
      "scene_number": 6,
      "text": "EXT. BROKEN SECTION \u2013 CONTINUOUS\n\n[00:09:00]\n\nA large portion of the bridge has collapsed, leaving a terrifying gap.\n\nClouds swirl violently below.\n\nROOK\n(grinning nervously)\nI live for moments like this.\n\nHe anchors a rope. One by one, they cross.\n\nMidway\u2014\n\nThe rope SLIPS.\n\nTavi dangles, panicking.\n\nTAVI\nI\u2019m slipping! I\u2019m slipping!\n\nArjun grabs him \u2014 muscles straining.\n\nARJUN\nLook at me. Not the clouds.\n\nThey pull Tavi up.\n\nSilence.\n\nThen relieved laughter.",
