      "scene_number": 7,
      "text": "EXT. SKYBRIDGE \u2013 STORM APPROACHING\n\n[00:13:00]\n\nDark clouds roll in fast. Wind intensifies.\n\nLightning flickers inside the clouds \u2014 silent but threatening.\n\nMIRA\nStorms weren\u2019t in the forecast.\n\nARJUN\nThis place makes its own rules.\n\nThey push forward.",
