      "scene_number": 8,
      "text": "EXT. ANCIENT OBSERVATORY \u2013 ON THE BRIDGE\n\n[00:16:00]\n\nA circular stone structure sits at the center of the bridge.\n\nInside: murals showing travelers crossing \u2014 some reaching the end, some falling.\n\nMIRA\n(quietly)\nThe bridge doesn\u2019t kill people\u2026 fear does.\n\nA sudden GUST blows debris inside.\n\nThe exit door SLAMS shut.",
