      "scene_id": "scene_009",
      "scene_number": 9,
      "text": "INT. OBSERVATORY \u2013 CONTINUOUS\n\n[00:18:00]\n\nThe floor lights up. Symbols rotate.\n\nA MECHANISM activates.\n\nTAVI\nIt\u2019s\u2026 a test?\n\nARJUN\nA choice.\n\nThree paths illuminate on the floor.\n\nMIRA\nOnly one is safe.\n\nThey debate. Tension rises.\n\nFinally\u2014\n\nARJUN\nWe go together. Same path.\n\nThey step forward.\n\nThe other paths COLLAPSE.\n\nThe door opens.",
