      "scene_id": "scene_010",
      "scene_number": 10,
      "text": "EXT. FINAL STRETCH OF SKYBRIDGE \u2013 SUN BREAKING THROUGH\n\n[00:22:00]\n\nThe storm clears suddenly.\n\nAhead: the LAST PILLAR, glowing with ancient energy.\n\nGolden light floods the bridge.\n\nROOK\nWorth it.\n\nAs they approach, the bridge begins to DISINTEGRATE behind them.\n\nThey RUN.\n\nStone CRUMBLES.\n\nLeaps. Slides. Near-falls.",
