      "text": "EXT. LAST PILLAR \u2013 CONTINUOUS\n\n[00:26:00]\n\nThey reach safety just as the bridge collapses completely.\n\nSilence.\n\nThe clouds below settle.\n\nThe pillar HUMS softly.\n\nMIRA\nIt\u2019s not treasure\u2026\n\nThe pillar projects visions \u2014 knowledge, maps, forgotten routes across the world.\n\nMIRA (CONT\u2019D)\nIt\u2019s a guide.",
